Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.49,0:00:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what I do, I can't stop loving Ryuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.07,0:00:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want him to be with Minorin,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.28,0:00:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's just too painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.01,0:00:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts. It really hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.60,0:00:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.88,0:00:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.04,0:00:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.57,0:00:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.27,0:00:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was half asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.33,0:00:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.03,0:00:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This all must be very traumatic for you, considering you're such good friends with Aisaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.31,0:00:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you just had a nightmare, Takasu-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.55,0:00:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let me remind you that the printout is due tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.68,0:00:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll repeat it again for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.00,0:01:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.01,0:01:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.09,0:01:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.93,0:01:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stop here for today.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:09.63,0:01:15.09,Ep Titles,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\fs52.5\pos(909.090909,526.5)}The Scene With You
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.55,0:01:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, we weren't seriously injured, and the rescue team saved us;
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.30,0:01:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then Taiga's real mother came to pick her up at the resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you contact her?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.39,0:01:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.56,0:01:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The teacher told me that Aisaka isn't doing so great,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.27,0:01:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so she's resting at her parents' place...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.28,0:01:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear anything about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I couldn't reach her cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.24,0:01:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.91,0:01:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a favor to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.17,0:01:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretend that you're the one who saved Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.38,0:02:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Taiga asks about it, tell her she was unconscious the whole time and said nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.47,0:02:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this related to the favor Taiga asked me on New Year's?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.15,0:02:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go out somewhere nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.66,0:02:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's eat some good food!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.29,0:02:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let Taiga be the only thing on your{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.71,0:02:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.46,0:02:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.84,0:02:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't the people inside taking a bit too long?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu, I'm not keeping you from cooking dinner, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.64,0:02:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for forcing you to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay; I won't go home until I taste the food here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to go home either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My parents will just ask what I'm going to do with my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to be so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This career assessment is just so they can decide how to split up the classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.74,0:03:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Notocchi, you're going into liberal arts, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I want to go into liberal arts and become an editor for a music magazine,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then finally become a freeloader.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be happy just to graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll have to work for my dad anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for being surprised, but you guys are actually thinking about your futures...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taka-chan, you're smart enough that you won't have any problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going into sciences, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be easy for you and Master Kitamura to pass the national testing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really, I still haven't decided if I'm going to college{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, next!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, find a seat and sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how's it going? Have you checked on her yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.67,0:03:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda, of course{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.77,0:03:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liberal arts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kushieda, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm working.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What about club activities?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're already over because daytime is shorter in winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what kind of noodles do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I'll poke your eyes out if you say a hottie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Ikimen" is Japanese slang for a hottie, a play on words for "ramen".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.14,0:04:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hottie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, three ramen please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, good choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three ramen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another new job, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the hourly wage is pretty nice, so I'll try two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have so many jo{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to open his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open his eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.84,0:04:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Endless Circle of Transmigration!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, please come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She never changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We would never have guessed she rejected you if you hadn't told us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls are such unpredictable creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, how are things going with Maya-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.34,0:05:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's still ignoring me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl's feelings, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.53,0:05:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she not back because she's really not feeling well,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or is her mother being selfish like her father and not letting her come?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}I can't stop...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...did she realize I heard her say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}...loving Ryuuji.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Career assessment?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just put something like "I'll study hard" and you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I make it to a four year college, how much money do you think it'll cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right; don't worry about money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, fermented soybean bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.49,0:06:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're different from me because you're smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After receiving a good education,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your talents will launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.75,0:06:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be able to live a wonderful life!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, isn't there a saying{\fscx301.8868}-{\fscx100.62893} what was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, gold jewel... something polish...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:07:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Golden stone... shining or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A jewel won't shine if it isn't polished"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.38,0:07:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuu-chan, you're like shining when you study!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I work and make around fifty thousand a month...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no working!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.66,0:07:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Working at Inage-san's is just an exception within an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.25,0:07:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to study if you work, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, we won't be able to have dinner together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A life like that is pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be happy at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you always tell me to go to college{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! There's always a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's always been like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, you're no different from other children even if you don't have a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an amazing mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be perfectly happy forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.38,0:08:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfectly happy forever, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga said before that she's on good terms with her real mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's probably happy to be around her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.37,0:08:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kushieda.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Takasu, you're here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're here for the budget estimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I'll turn it in later!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:08:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll be counting on you, new team captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, the new Student Council President is sure busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,New team captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you already the team captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Kitamura's student council is really busy,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so they merged the male and the female softball team,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I was appointed the new team captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll probably become as busy as Kitamura-kun because I'm unlucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Then why are you getting another job?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't that make you busier?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you heard the saying that young people must endure hardship, Takasu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't that hinder both sides{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm working hard because I don't want to hinder anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because it's something that can be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something that can be seen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.10,0:09:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's A-min!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're beautiful as usual today!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that attitude, Kawashima?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:09:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come near me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:09:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupidity is contagious, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.03,0:10:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the child is not here, the father can do anything he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.46,0:10:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Kawashima?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later, Takasu-kun! I'm going too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, class is about to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you plan to skip first?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why must it be you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.24,0:10:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to tell you this a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is there left to say after all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, there's a...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.06,0:10:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ghost in that gap!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.30,0:10:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears between those two vending machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it was a heartbroken girl who took her{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell me earlier?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.22,0:11:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But nothing has happened so far, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.02,0:11:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think ghosts have their own personality too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.02,0:11:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll only appear in front of people who they want to see and understand them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.57,0:11:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I've seen a ghost before, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to yearn and get caught by something I can't see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and lose the things I can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You talk too much, I don't want to hear the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll understand after you've heard the whole thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.55,0:11:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to say that if I just watch and don't interfere, everything will turn out fine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, talking to you feels like having a period.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't hesitate anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will look forward and try to get what I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:11:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, shut up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:12:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't hesitate anymore, I swear! I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.61,0:12:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is about your career assessment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I still haven't talked to my family about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then do you still feel the same as at the beginning of this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an overachieving student and I expect a lot from you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that's why I'm concerned over this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how being a teacher is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.65,0:12:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't have expectations in me; my family is poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the problem is financial?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you need it, there are different scholarships and financial aids{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it strange to not go to college?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that I couldn't tell with just this career assessment...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:12:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How you feel about it, not how others feel about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why is it so dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.51,0:13:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:20.15,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\an8\fad(400,0)}I found a part-time job, I'll be going to the shop after work from now on. Love, Yasuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Job?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what she means by "It's all right! There's always a way!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't she also say it'd be pointless if a mother and son didn't have dinner together?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuu-chan, you're like shining when you study!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.31,0:14:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I give it to her now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}How is a love letter embarrassing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Disgusting, isn't it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Since I don't have the guts to confess to her, I just have to imagine like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}It's horribly miserable, but I don't think of it as embarrassing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, the feeling of liking someone is not embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say that to the person who likes me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.84,0:14:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't say it even if I want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, she's not answering my calls!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, why are you work{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.90,0:14:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-T-T-T{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you and who were you with?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:15:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You nearly killed me. You idiot, pig, dog, yaksha, asura, gorilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No running!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You tried to strangle me and look at me with weird eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was just surprised because you appeared out of nowhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You didn't even call me. I was really worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the battery died.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.61,0:15:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to explain everything to me in detail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.11,0:15:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you didn't come back because you{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why did I say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.04,0:15:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wound isn't that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.87,0:15:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing about me not doing so great was a lie. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to skip school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see, so you're all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hadn't seen my mom for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We stayed at a hotel,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we went shopping, and to restaurants and movies and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just being a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let me in first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say you weren't going to come over anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.15,0:16:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost my keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go in through the window from your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use the three-second rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Can you do it within three seconds?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for intruding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.33,0:16:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why don't you have dinner here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are some fermented beans left, so I'll just add some onions{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, I already had dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.71,0:16:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh yeah, Inko-chan wants to say hi to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's his new greeting! He learned it recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did that ugly bird get fatter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.35,0:16:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Exactly! It's because you're not here to stress him{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scratch that! He's eating too much because he's so lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:16:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's as ugly as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, being with Taiga is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ryuuj{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.67,0:17:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.63,0:17:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I wasn't crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just yawning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. It's late, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.26,0:17:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, ugly one. I'm leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... This is actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just cleaning out stuff because I had time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I didn't have time at the end of last year...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.95,0:17:38.20,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really clumsy, but I finally understood after what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I'm clumsy, I can still be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop thinking about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you find out Minorin's true feelings yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:17:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you didn't ask her because of the fuss I caused...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she worrying about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:09.60,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise I won't be clumsy anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.65,0:18:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things will definitely turn out fine between you and Minorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ryuuji! Don't just stand there, come and help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.59,0:18:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always forget to lock the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.26,0:18:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A highly secured mansion isn't always convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, be careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.15,0:18:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I nearly forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:18:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.61,0:19:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, Kitamura-kun and Minorin went to look for me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.75,0:19:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't remember, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.46,0:19:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you were unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but I had a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.21,0:19:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my dreams, Kitamura-kun was carrying me on his back,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I muttered something stupid to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.68,0:19:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a dream, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something stupid, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does she want to pretend she didn't say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura-kun did carry you on his back,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you didn't say anything because you were unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I heard, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
